txt.en: You have been tasked with defeating ukhrâsh and plugging leaks in Gundabad.
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Ausma for your reward!

'I have a new mission for you, [placeholder].

'Some workers have just returned from Shalakâm where they were to make repairs to the tunnels, and it seems they only narrowly escaped a horde of ukhrâsh! It does not surprise me that beasts would roam the ancient, flooded waterways of Gundabad. What surprises me is the shear number of these beasts!

'You are to travel to Shalakâm, clear the waterways of the ukhrâsh, and help with the repairs! For Gundabad!'

'Within Shalakâm, the ancient waterways of Gundabad, the ukhrâsh have roamed unchecked. Their years of clawing and digging threaten to collapse the ancient tunnels….\n\n'Your mission is to defeat ukhrâsh and plug leaks in Gundabad.'
Monsters in this mission will apply a corruption buff to nearby allies.
Your mission is to defeat ukhrâsh and plug leaks in Gundabad.\n\nSpeak to Ausma to travel.

'Excellent work, [placeholder]!\n\n'With the ukhrash horde defeated and repairs to the waterways underway, I hope to see the old tunnels restored and safe again soon. If the ukhrâsh return, we will be ready for them!'
